{"tid":2397620,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你中學啲MK而家做緊咩?","createTime":"2021-02-06T14:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T21:51:49.000Z","uid":198401,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef56aa241fafb68205f461fc12df2f82c7dad41","tid":2397620,"uid":198401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:48:08.000Z","msg":"識得有個有腹肌 運動叻<br />\n初中嗰陣時蝦蝦霸霸<br />\n學校好多女都冧佢<br />\n啲女半個月換一件咁滯<br />\n雖然條友咁MK<br />\n但又唔知點解好多friend<br />\n個個人都驚佢同時又好似崇拜佢咁(包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n去到中三升中四就退咗學<br />\n15定16歲就衰十一<br />\n而家個仔都幾歲<br />\n行街見到佢諗住同佢打聲招呼<br />\n但佢又頭耷耷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8fb0f9663c057f4d472ef01fd41b74f738afa7","tid":2397620,"uid":391202,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ec1eeb93b6d32747b1e31e4af6850a2eb8b416d","tid":2397620,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"做狗"},{"pid":"438ae76a02d7f7d335c68f335b6f61c6c3b769f1","tid":2397620,"uid":198401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee8fb0f9663c057f4d472ef01fd41b74f738afa7","tid":2397620,"uid":391202,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"Sor9 唔好fb公審我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初我都有加入你個家族<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都叫做過哎吔兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hk